Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.57,0:00:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.70,0:00:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to do business here,\Nget a state permit first.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.12,0:00:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlicensed prostitutes are trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.37,0:00:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't make much money\Nif I do it legally.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.04,0:00:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.42,0:00:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If I have his permission,\Nit'll be okay. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.55,0:00:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.63,0:00:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Him? Who are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.10,0:00:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll keep coming here\Nuntil you let me see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.97,0:00:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The man they call the "Baby."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.16,0:02:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't use your hands to catch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.12,0:02:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not a goalkeeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.95,0:02:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Rules don't apply to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.79,0:02:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did he go anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.54,0:02:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.71,0:02:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.79,0:02:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He told me to stay with you for a while
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.34,0:02:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,because he found the man\Nhe was looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.01,0:02:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying that he wants me\Nto look after you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.39,0:02:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hah! Don't be absurd!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.51,0:03:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate kids! That Tenma…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.52,0:03:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't get a hold of him,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.19,0:03:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and now he's got some mystery kid in tow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.02,0:03:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to our plan of getting rich\Nfrom him being an underground doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.90,0:03:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He's got to start working seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.32,0:03:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.66,0:03:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice header!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.24,0:03:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you little…\NWhat did you do that for? You brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.74,0:03:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I said you can't touch the ball\Nwith your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.33,0:03:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,A yellow card for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.50,0:03:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! How can I live in this world\Nif I'm scared of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.71,0:03:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If you keep saying that,\Nyou'll get a red card.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.00,0:03:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.30,0:03:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,FRANKFURT CENTRAL STATION
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.00,0:04:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.92,0:04:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me the stuff now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.42,0:04:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry and give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.26,0:04:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while, Detective Messener.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.72,0:04:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,D… Doctor Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.56,0:04:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.52,0:04:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You called me that back then as well,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.65,0:04:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,even though we had just met and you\Nnever asked what my profession was.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.48,0:04:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I'm no longer a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.36,0:04:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which,\Nyou are no longer a detective, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.12,0:04:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,"Officer discharged for possession\Nof narcotics."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.54,0:04:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I was surprised when I found this article\Nfrom six months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.83,0:04:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd advise you not to stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.34,0:04:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.25,0:04:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a gun pointing at you\Nunder my coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.97,0:05:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh… what do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.64,0:05:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to ask you about what you did\Nin Heidelberg ten months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.14,0:05:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, I want to know\Nwho hired you for the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.11,0:05:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I… I don't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.23,0:05:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You took the lives of the Fortners
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.36,0:05:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and the journalist, Mr. Maurer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.28,0:05:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't do it! I was only the lookout.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.87,0:05:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,My partner, Müller, did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.12,0:05:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Detective Müller quit\Nright after the incident, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.54,0:05:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Y… Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.75,0:05:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He got a lot of money for that and\Nis probably living it up right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.42,0:05:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But you spent all your money on drugs,\Nand this is how you ended up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.93,0:05:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He was the only one who accepted the job\Nand did the deed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.56,0:05:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And he was the one who received\Nmost of the payment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.27,0:05:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone even once tried to kill me\Nto keep me quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.52,0:05:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised you survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.53,0:05:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I was saved by a certain organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.57,0:06:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Organization?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.90,0:06:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this enough? Just leave me be.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.70,0:06:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I talked too much the other day, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.83,0:06:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The other day? To whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.83,0:06:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave me alone!\NI don't have time for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.83,0:06:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're suffering from withdrawal symptoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.00,0:06:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But as long as I'm sitting here,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.01,0:06:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think the dealer will\Ncome near you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.01,0:06:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I… I told you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.76,0:06:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I was saved by the Baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.35,0:06:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Baby"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.27,0:06:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to the bar called "Candy."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.64,0:06:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you will meet him there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.06,0:06:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is the "Baby"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.98,0:06:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a major far-right figure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.48,0:06:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He has a role in two rightist parties.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.03,0:06:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The Baby went to the east side\Nafter the Wall fell,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.87,0:06:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and he tried to build a town\Nof pure Germans.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.20,0:06:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But he failed, so he came back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.33,0:06:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did that man save you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.00,0:06:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The darkness…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.09,0:07:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,When the Berlin Wall fell,\Na great darkness was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.93,0:07:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,A monster… was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.47,0:07:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.43,0:07:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Just go away!\NI told that girl everything already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.69,0:07:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.11,0:07:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,She came for revenge\Nand pointed a gun at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.11,0:07:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the daughter of the couple\Nwe killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.49,0:07:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Anna?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.41,0:07:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.83,0:07:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Nina Fortner come to see you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.45,0:07:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The Baby told me
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.54,0:07:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,if that girl came to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.04,0:07:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to tell her to go see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.09,0:07:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He said the girl is an important bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.84,0:07:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,An important… bait?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.85,0:07:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.56,0:07:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You do have patience,\Ncoming here every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.90,0:08:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,How about I buy you\Nfor the night at a good price?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.44,0:08:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You said I'd be in trouble\Nif I worked here
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.49,0:08:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,without the Baby's approval.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.45,0:08:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you little!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.20,0:08:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is that look?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.62,0:08:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she the one who wanted\Nto see the Baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.54,0:08:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh… Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.88,0:08:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This way, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.09,0:08:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.66,0:08:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.54,0:08:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stand on the mark and wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.59,0:09:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no. Right over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.38,0:09:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.58,0:09:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know this song?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.29,0:09:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't help but feel like dancing\Nto the pleasant rhythm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.29,0:09:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Nina Fortner.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.93,0:09:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The Baby said it himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.64,0:10:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This country would be fine\Nif only a second Hitler was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.06,0:10:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl is the bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.32,0:10:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.28,0:10:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.49,0:10:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I know everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.12,0:10:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You had another name, Anna Liebert.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.41,0:10:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's not your real name, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.12,0:10:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Names have so very little meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.50,0:10:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, my name is the Baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.00,0:10:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on and dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.59,0:10:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that you know\Nwhere I can find my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.13,0:10:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Johan? That's a good name.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.60,0:10:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So you do know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.72,0:10:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do when you see\Nyour brother, dressed like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.06,0:10:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.40,0:10:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't wave a dangerous thing\Nlike that around.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.86,0:10:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.16,0:10:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Johan will show up to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.59,0:11:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I used to live here\Nwhen I was a kid,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.84,0:11:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I even know the back alleys in this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.88,0:11:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a pawn shop ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.14,0:11:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We will pawn this carpet for some cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.89,0:11:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You don't have money, Mr. Heckel?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.68,0:11:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! I have got to do something\Nto get money for your dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.15,0:11:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be grateful!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.90,0:11:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.65,0:11:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.78,0:11:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What the…?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.74,0:11:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.70,0:11:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This area has become a Turkish district.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.25,0:11:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.00,0:11:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This is fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.88,0:11:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What… What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.13,0:11:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this pattern and texture.\NThis is hand-woven silk, for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.26,0:11:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No, this is synthetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.93,0:12:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I feel sorry for you,\NI'll take it for 100 marks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.14,0:12:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This is why I hate this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.89,0:12:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,If this store was still owned by a German,\NI would've got 10,000 marks!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.48,0:12:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Then take it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.07,0:12:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,After I'm gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.07,0:12:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,don't come looking for me\Nwhen you realize it's real!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.32,0:12:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what a real one should look like.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.53,0:12:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a 100% silk Hereke carpet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.08,0:12:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a closer look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.95,0:12:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the small, fine details\Nare elegantly done.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.63,0:12:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's worth 150,000 marks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.88,0:12:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That has to be fake!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.75,0:12:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't even have the expertise\Nto see that my carpet is real!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.13,0:12:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Dieter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.56,0:12:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.27,0:12:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,-It was real.\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.86,0:12:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the real thing,\Nand it's worth 150,000 marks?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.28,0:12:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If we know where to sell it,\Nwe could get 800,000 marks!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.11,0:13:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's eat something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.57,0:13:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Once we get that thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.33,0:13:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,we will get to eat whatever we want!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.33,0:13:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you going to get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.79,0:13:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.42,0:13:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh… Why are you looking\Nat me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.38,0:13:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.47,0:13:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, stupid! Keep it down, you brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.48,0:13:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.44,0:13:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but look for other clients.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.82,0:13:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.11,0:13:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,An Asian man like you\Nwandering around here
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.95,0:13:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,could get killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.99,0:13:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That place is a base\Nfor right-wing people.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.53,0:13:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you Turkish?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.62,0:13:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you do your business around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.33,0:13:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you talking about?\NWhy would I work in this dump?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.67,0:13:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,My friend was taken by the men in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.09,0:14:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, she found out\Na secret about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.76,0:14:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,A secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.13,0:14:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.80,0:14:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to get her out of there.\NI'm afraid of what they're doing to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.39,0:14:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,A woman I know is in there too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.02,0:14:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of woman?\NIs it a girl with long blonde hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.61,0:14:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure what kind\Nof hair she has now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.61,0:14:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's her, then she was just\Ntaken away in a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.20,0:14:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.66,0:14:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.37,0:14:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Baby was with her,\Nso she's probably at his house.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.33,0:14:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The Baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.58,0:14:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of car was it? What color?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.58,0:14:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a big, bright red Mercedes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.29,0:14:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. I'll just have to find the car\Nand go after them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.46,0:14:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Please save my friend, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.55,0:14:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! She has a little child waiting\Nfor her at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.43,0:14:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.20,0:15:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Not dead, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.66,0:15:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,This way, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.12,0:15:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Before you go in,\Nlet me take your gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.67,0:15:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, please go in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.52,0:15:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit wherever you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.28,0:15:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you the girl the Baby brought here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.86,0:15:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.08,0:15:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, you're quite a beautiful girl indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.46,0:15:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a surprise,\Nsince you're Johan's twin sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.30,0:16:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Professor Goedelitz.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.30,0:16:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The one in the photo with Johan\Nis General Wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.31,0:16:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The two of us and two others\Nare in control of the organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.52,0:16:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,How about fruit? Would you like some?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.65,0:16:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother… Please let me see Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.20,0:16:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You will see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.70,0:16:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Once he knows that you're here,\Nhe will definitely come.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.74,0:16:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He needs you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.71,0:16:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose you don't know where Johan is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.21,0:16:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We need him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.38,0:16:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We need him to be at the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.47,0:16:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know why Hitler was\Nable to have so much power?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.02,0:16:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He was smart, with a mind for business.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.48,0:16:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He understood these three points.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.44,0:17:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He controlled the banks, won over the arms\Nindustry, and seized the military.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.70,0:17:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, Johan is lying in wait\Nwithin one of those.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.66,0:17:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,How about it?\NDon't you think my reasoning is correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.71,0:17:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you do with Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.54,0:17:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,However, it was Hitler's charisma\Nthat allowed him to achieve it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.22,0:17:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitler failed to get into art school, 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.09,0:17:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,then couldn't advance\Nbeyond corporal in the military.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.89,0:17:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He finally revealed his charisma,\Nonly after the age of thirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.06,0:17:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But what about Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.35,0:17:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since he was a child,\Nhe had enormous charisma.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.69,0:17:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost like another Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.20,0:17:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But you must not forget one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.57,0:17:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The first ones to put faith in Christ\Nwere the Three Magi
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.83,0:18:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and John the Baptist, four amazing people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.91,0:18:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The four of us have paid close attention\Nto Johan's talent since his childhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.96,0:18:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that wonderful?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.30,0:18:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.01,0:18:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like you to stay here for a while
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.55,0:18:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,until Johan comes to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.43,0:18:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd also like you not to try to escape
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.06,0:18:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,since you have already\Nstepped one foot in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.02,0:18:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry about that.\NI'm here because I want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.07,0:18:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll wait for Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.74,0:18:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That'd be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.95,0:18:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, have some fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.96,0:18:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you have finally come around.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.26,0:18:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.22,0:18:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have any broken bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.93,0:18:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.06,0:19:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.43,0:19:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.81,0:19:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one asking questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.57,0:19:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You only have to answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.19,0:19:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.95,0:19:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do\Nafter you find Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.28,0:19:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.74,0:19:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you I'm the one\Nasking the questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.12,0:19:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing with Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.75,0:19:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I already said no questions from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.00,0:19:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina is our important guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.76,0:19:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not trash like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.51,0:19:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Then she's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.39,0:19:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,For now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.55,0:19:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But that girl is dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.72,0:19:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,She has such a pretty face,\Nbut she's trying to kill Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.19,0:19:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Those kinds of people have to\Nbe disposed of eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.98,0:19:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So Nina is just a bait to lure Johan, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.57,0:19:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you people?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.28,0:19:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.90,0:19:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Another question?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.28,0:20:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You foreign races have\Nno right to ask questions!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.95,0:20:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That kind of impertinent attitude will\Nsend this whole district up in flames!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.38,0:20:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The… district?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.55,0:20:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. The sky tomorrow night will be\Ndyed with a beautiful color.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.02,0:20:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I will see Johan if I stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.81,0:21:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Help…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.23,0:21:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Please help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.82,0:21:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.11,0:21:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He… Help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.07,0:21:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.70,0:21:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The third floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.91,0:21:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You speak in broken German.\NWhere are you from?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.58,0:21:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Turkish… They will kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.63,0:21:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.80,0:21:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose the people here have\Nimprisoned you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.93,0:21:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Help.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.55,0:21:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have to stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.26,0:21:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Please help.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.35,0:21:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone needs to warn them soon,\Nor else my son will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.07,0:21:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow night, we are having\Na welcome party for Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.61,0:22:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Superior races like ours should be\Nthe only ones to exist in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.37,0:22:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The rest can all be burned.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.37,0:22:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I accidentally overheard the men talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.83,0:22:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They're going to start\Na fire tomorrow night.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.30,0:22:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They're planning to\Nburn down the Turkish District.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.72,0:22:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Help! Help!
